<i>Episode 16</i>

5
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,879
Starting today,

6
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:41,079
you're just a slave in the Eagle Army.

7
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,079
What do you want me to do?

8
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:52,359
I want you to disappear from Tang.

9
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:55,200
I have the final say in deciding whether I'm dead or not.

10
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,840
What you say is useless.

11
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,920
That depends on your capability.

12
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:02,000
Keeping me by your side...

13
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,040
is like raising a tiger.

14
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,560
It makes no difference.

15
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,719
Make sure you survive first...

16
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:07,959
before you are worried about that.

17
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,120
The law of survival on the grasslands...

18
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:13,680
is only the strongest survives.

19
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,400
Behind me...

20
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:56,240
is Shuozhuo...

21
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,919
that has been looted but the people escaped the battle unscathed.

22
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,599
Behind it...

23
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:04,400
is endless mountains.

24
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,000
Beyond that...

25
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:10,319
is my homeland, a million miles away.

26
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,240
Chang'an.

27
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,960
In the end, I couldn't go back there.

28
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,960
In the past, you achieved glory for the motherland.

29
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,360
Now, you're just a slave.

30
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,280
Li Chang Ge.

31
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:33,120
Even I feel bad for you.

32
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:39,479
<i>Fuju Inn</i>

33
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:40,599
After receiving the order,

34
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:41,919
I hurried here right away.

35
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:42,919
Please give me your instructions, Commander Hao.

36
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,199
Follow Ashina Tribe at once.

37
00:03:45,479 --> 00:03:47,520
I want to know what happened to Li Chang Ge in the end.

38
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,560
Should I kill her?

39
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,520
If she colludes with Ashina Tribe,

40
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:53,639
kill her.

41
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:55,800
What if she doesn't?

42
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:57,680
Ashina Tribe won't keep her.

43
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,439
Yes.

44
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,120
Send whatever news you have...

45
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,159
through the pigeon.

46
00:04:04,199 --> 00:04:05,199
You may leave.

47
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,599
Yes.

48
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,319
The people dearest to me...

49
00:04:15,439 --> 00:04:17,560
were all slaughtered like pigs and dogs.

50
00:04:18,170 --> 00:04:19,800
The place I was born and raised...

51
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,480
banished me.

52
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:23,439
I felt like dying every single day.

53
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:26,610
But I had to do what I had to do.

54
00:04:28,199 --> 00:04:29,730
Once this is over,

55
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,199
it won't be too late to kill me.

56
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:35,360
<i>Noble and integrate</i>

57
00:04:35,759 --> 00:04:36,959
Li Chang Ge.

58
00:04:37,610 --> 00:04:39,730
I hope you can sacrifice for the people.

59
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,639
Recently,

60
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:47,279
all the county offices around the kingdom...

61
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:49,560
are secretly looking for the princess.

62
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,170
However, the portrait that was sent to the capital...

63
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:54,480
looks nothing like the princess.

64
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:57,639
Furthermore, the princess lost in the four states in the north.

65
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:58,639
Until now,

66
00:04:59,839 --> 00:05:02,000
we haven't heard anything yet.

67
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,800
Your Highness.

68
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:07,240
Princess Yong'an is very blessed.

69
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:10,319
Didn't Li Chun Feng make a prediction...

70
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:12,639
that she'll come back safely?

71
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,360
I hope so.

72
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:17,680
Lately,

73
00:05:18,959 --> 00:05:20,050
I always dreamed of...

74
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:22,399
Le Yan and Chang Ge when they were younger.

75
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,240
Both of them...

76
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,399
were hanging around in the garden.

77
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:29,600
I waved at them...

78
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:31,639
but they couldn't see me.

79
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:33,920
I called out their names.

80
00:05:34,319 --> 00:05:35,680
But they couldn't hear me either.

81
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,319
Worse,

82
00:05:37,439 --> 00:05:38,959
they kept running away.

83
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:45,040
Your Highness...

84
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,519
worries too much.

85
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:47,560
That's why...

86
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:50,000
Your Highness had weird dreams.

87
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:53,079
Your Highness, I'll get the imperial kitchen...

88
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:56,279
to make some soothing soup for Your Highness.

89
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,199
Will those two girls...

90
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,600
be further away from me?

91
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,480
No.

92
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:06,920
They will always be...

93
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,480
the most daring daughter and official to you.

94
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,480
Perhaps at this moment,

95
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,839
no news is the best news.

96
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,560
That's right.

97
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,800
Your Highness, there is urgent military news.

98
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,800
Ashina Tribe suddenly attacked the north border.

99
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:29,079
The chief commander, Sima Tu...

100
00:06:29,079 --> 00:06:31,120
and the governor of Shuozhou, Gongsun Heng...

101
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,720
were killed in the battle.

102
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,560
When did it happen?

103
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,199
No one reported it!

104
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:38,000
Ashina Tribe besieged the city.

105
00:06:38,279 --> 00:06:40,480
The frontier couldn't deliver the message.

106
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:43,560
Hao Du sent his men to speed things up.

107
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,160
Five horses were sacrificed...

108
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:47,160
before the news reached Chang'an.

109
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:50,360
Send our army there now to regain the north region.

110
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,920
Make sure we chase the Ashina Tribe out of the border.

111
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,439
After that,

112
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,879
the troops will camp at the same place...

113
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,240
to comfort the people in the north.

114
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,439
Yes, Your Highness.

115
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,000
Mr. Du.

116
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:06,839
Mr. Du.

117
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:10,160
I need to talk to you.

118
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:15,240
You always know your own mind.

119
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:17,439
What do you want to discuss with me?

120
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:19,800
Mr. Du, don't be sarcastic.

121
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:21,800
You and I are the ministers of the imperial court.

122
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:24,199
It's good to have someone to discuss with.

123
00:07:24,319 --> 00:07:25,639
Furthermore,

124
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,839
I really need a favor from you.

125
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,600
Just tell me what it is.

126
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,360
As you know,

127
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,120
Princess Yong'an is missing in action.

128
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,480
It's His Highness's biggest concern.

129
00:07:36,839 --> 00:07:37,920
The portrait of Princess Yong'an...

130
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,519
has been sent to all local government offices...

131
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,079
for a secret investigation.

132
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:42,199
However, Princess Yong'an is nowhere to be found.

133
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,000
But we didn't receive any news...

134
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,759
from the north.

135
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,560
I'm just worried.

136
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,519
What do you want me to do?

137
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,199
People in the north...

138
00:07:53,199 --> 00:07:55,560
have never seen Princess Yong'an before.

139
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:59,160
Your godson is in the north, right?

140
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:01,160
Although Wei Shu Yu...

141
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:04,199
allegedly lost her,

142
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,800
at that time,

143
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,079
your godson, Hao Du...

144
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:09,319
was with Princess Yong'an.

145
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,680
The more collaborative the effort,

146
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:12,439
the better.

147
00:08:12,639 --> 00:08:14,920
Furthermore, under your guidance,

148
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,920
- your godson is already... - That's enough.

149
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,759
Talk properly.

150
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:19,759
Don't flatter me.

151
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,040
Since His Highness...

152
00:08:22,199 --> 00:08:24,399
has entrusted you with this case,

153
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,199
you should work on it.

154
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:34,000
Yes.

155
00:08:35,210 --> 00:08:36,210
Eat up.

156
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,639
Here.

157
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,559
What's the point of keeping him here?

158
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:43,759
If you ask me, I'll just kill him.

159
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:46,000
- Hold on. - Here.

160
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:47,450
Leave it there.

161
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:50,450
Give me more.

162
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:51,759
Here.

163
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,279
Where are you going?

164
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,679
I didn't expect to see you here.

165
00:09:06,679 --> 00:09:07,720
Here.

166
00:09:11,450 --> 00:09:12,639
Actually, the Eagle Army...

167
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:14,000
isn't too far from Shuozhou.

168
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:16,090
It's near a river and there are trees.

169
00:09:16,090 --> 00:09:17,330
You'll get used to it.

170
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,399
Eat up.

171
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,090
Let me tell you.

172
00:09:23,090 --> 00:09:24,559
If His Highness didn't care about you,

173
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,039
I wouldn't care about you either.

174
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:27,960
My goodness.

175
00:09:32,210 --> 00:09:34,519
Your friend is insensible.

176
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:37,480
I think you're wasting your effort on him.

177
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,210
Look at that body.

178
00:09:39,399 --> 00:09:41,360
I don't think he can survive in the grasslands.

179
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,720
No, he'll survive.

180
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:43,960
How do you know that?

181
00:09:44,519 --> 00:09:46,450
He is someone who has a strong desire to live.

182
00:09:49,799 --> 00:09:50,840
He won't be defeated...

183
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:52,720
so easily.

184
00:09:53,210 --> 00:09:54,519
It looks like...

185
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:56,039
you know him very well.

186
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:57,600
But I think...

187
00:09:57,759 --> 00:09:59,840
you're just the enemy to him.

188
00:10:01,279 --> 00:10:02,330
It doesn't matter.

189
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:07,330
You've never treated me so nicely after all these years.

190
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:25,399
That person...

191
00:10:25,559 --> 00:10:26,799
has been following us for a long time.

192
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,879
I know.

193
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,519
He's here to see Shi Si Lang.

194
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,879
Do something for me.

195
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,639
What are you doing?

196
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:40,799
Let go!

197
00:10:41,279 --> 00:10:42,360
Listen to me.

198
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,919
You're our slave.

199
00:10:43,919 --> 00:10:45,480
Just do whatever I tell you to do.

200
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,000
What?

201
00:10:47,279 --> 00:10:48,559
Are you refusing to work?

202
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:50,639
You must have a death wish.

203
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:52,639
Take him away.

204
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:53,840
Cut him into pieces and feed him to the dogs!

205
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,000
- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.

206
00:10:57,039 --> 00:10:58,120
What are you doing?

207
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,200
What are you doing?

208
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,399
Let go of me!

209
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,200
Let go!

210
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,759
Come on!

211
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:04,840
Let go!

212
00:11:07,879 --> 00:11:08,879
Come on!

213
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,720
Elder Qin.

214
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:47,759
I feel bad for Yuan Niang.

215
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,720
She has been homeless and travels with us for so long.

216
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,639
Not at all.

217
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:56,559
She has the best father and mother in the world.

218
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,320
How is Shuozhou doing?

219
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,000
I heard that...

220
00:12:03,159 --> 00:12:04,600
the Ashina Tribe has left.

221
00:12:05,159 --> 00:12:07,440
Someone from the imperial court will come and take over the rest.

222
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:09,759
Aside from that...

223
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:12,559
"Aside from that"?

224
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,919
Are you going to tell me...

225
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,600
about Young Master?

226
00:12:16,919 --> 00:12:18,879
He failed in the assassination.

227
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:19,879
He was killed.

228
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:23,200
I see. He's...

229
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,159
He's too strong and impulsive.

230
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,519
It's easy to destroy those who are strong and impulsive.

231
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:29,320
If...

232
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:33,320
Stop it.

233
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:35,000
I think Young Master...

234
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,679
is still alive.

235
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,600
He's still alive?

236
00:12:38,919 --> 00:12:40,879
Since Ashina Sun...

237
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,080
made a promise with Governor Gongsun,

238
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,240
he won't kill him for sure.

239
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:48,480
Perhaps he has brought him to the grasslands.

240
00:12:48,879 --> 00:12:50,200
Let's not wait any longer.

241
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:52,159
- Let's look for him. - In the grasslands,

242
00:12:52,159 --> 00:12:54,080
they have spies everywhere.

243
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:56,840
We can't barge in as we like.

244
00:12:58,759 --> 00:13:00,759
Let's take care of Yuan Niang first.

245
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:03,440
We should use our previous connection...

246
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,679
and see if we can get some information.

247
00:13:05,679 --> 00:13:06,759
Then I'll make a decision.

248
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:21,960
<i>Someone has been executed by Ashina Sun.</i>

249
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,159
Li Chang Ge.

250
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:31,679
Perhaps this is the best place for you.

251
00:13:50,039 --> 00:13:51,080
Why are you here?

252
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,159
That's my question for you.

253
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,840
Losing the princess is a serious matter...

254
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,759
yet His Highness didn't blame you.

255
00:13:58,279 --> 00:13:59,919
I'll find Le Yan for sure.

256
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,039
I'll wait and see.

257
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:04,519
It has been so long.

258
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:05,799
You didn't return to Chang'an.

259
00:14:06,799 --> 00:14:08,039
Are you looking for Chang Ge?

260
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,480
What happened to her?

261
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,240
She's dead.

262
00:14:16,039 --> 00:14:17,200
How did she die?

263
00:14:18,759 --> 00:14:19,840
Did you kill her?

264
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:24,240
Tell me!

265
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,639
Wei Shu Yu.

266
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:39,039
Do you plan to sacrifice yourself and your family...

267
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:41,039
just to avenge your lover?

268
00:14:41,159 --> 00:14:42,360
After killing you,

269
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:45,159
I'll kill myself to atone for it.

270
00:14:45,159 --> 00:14:47,000
Do you think that His Highness...

271
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:49,360
will punish the Wei family just for you?

272
00:14:51,759 --> 00:14:52,960
Then why didn't you do it?

273
00:14:54,279 --> 00:14:56,000
When Li Chang Ge was alive, you couldn't do anything.

274
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,039
Now that she's dead,

275
00:14:57,159 --> 00:14:58,240
you found the courage to take revenge.

276
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,279
I guess,

277
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:03,639
that's because you know that since Li Chang Ge is dead,

278
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:05,879
your family's glory won't be affected.

279
00:15:13,879 --> 00:15:15,279
Even if you want revenge,

280
00:15:15,279 --> 00:15:16,399
you've come to the wrong person.

281
00:15:17,399 --> 00:15:18,679
I didn't kill Li Chang Ge.

