578
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:06,359
Young lady!

579
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:08,200
I'm an honorable man.

580
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,039
It's three cents for a cookie.

581
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:11,920
I won't ask for anything else.

582
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:14,640
No. I'm afraid that someone else might steal it.

583
00:31:14,799 --> 00:31:16,920
That's why I keep my pouch in the innermost layer.

584
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:20,920
I see.

585
00:31:29,799 --> 00:31:31,720
