587
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:37,000
I think...

588
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:39,640
this is the prettiest pouch.

589
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:47,559
All right. Hold on.

590
00:31:50,839 --> 00:31:52,400
Here's your cookie.

591
00:31:54,359 --> 00:31:55,680
- Thank you. - All right.

592
00:31:58,559 --> 00:31:59,599
Hey.

593
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:13,039
I'm sorry.

594
00:32:13,039 --> 00:32:14,079
It's all right.

595
00:32:14,079 --> 00:32:16,119
I've had something dirtier before.

596
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:20,359
If you don't mind,

597
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:22,279
I'll give you half.

598
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,799
I'll give you some.

599
00:32:28,119 --> 00:32:29,759
- I didn't mean any harm. - Hey.

600
00:32:29,759 --> 00:32:30,839
Nowadays,

601
00:32:31,039 --> 00:32:32,680
