602
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:35,400
What are you waiting for? You should check your pouch.

603
00:32:35,599 --> 00:32:37,720
You even thought of sharing the food with him.

604
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:39,400
You must be a fool.

605
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:42,319
Come and take a look.

606
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:45,480
My pouch.

607
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:47,079
My pouch!

608
00:32:48,519 --> 00:32:49,680
Stop right there!

609
00:32:51,359 --> 00:32:52,400
Stop right there!

610
00:32:53,799 --> 00:32:55,559
My pouch!

611
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,720
Stop right there!

612
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:02,799
Stop right there!

613
00:33:14,319 --> 00:33:15,400
Stop right there!

614
00:33:17,440 --> 00:33:18,640
Give me back my pouch.

615
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,839
You can take the money.

616
00:33:38,039 --> 00:33:39,119
Right.

617
00:33:39,119 --> 00:33:40,279
Here. This is for you.

618
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:45,559
It's so ugly. What's this?

619
00:33:45,559 --> 00:33:47,079
My hands got pricked in order to make that,

620
00:33:47,079 --> 00:33:48,200
and you're even complaining that it's ugly.

621
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:50,799
- Forget it then. - It is ugly,

622
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:52,319
but I like it.

623
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,039
Chang Ge.

624
00:34:01,839 --> 00:34:03,119
Where are you?

625
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:16,960
Have you seen the lady...

626
00:34:17,119 --> 00:34:18,119
on the portrait?

627
00:34:18,289 --> 00:34:19,289
No.

628
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:21,769
Have you seen this lady?

629
00:34:21,769 --> 00:34:22,769
No.

630
00:34:24,039 --> 00:34:25,119
This lady in the portrait,

631
00:34:25,329 --> 00:34:26,400
have you seen her before?

632
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,400
No.

633
00:34:29,079 --> 00:34:30,809
- Have you seen her before? - No.

634
00:34:31,199 --> 00:34:32,289
You!

635
00:34:32,639 --> 00:34:34,199
- No, I haven't seen her. - Are they...

636
00:34:34,199 --> 00:34:35,519
Are they after me?

637
00:34:40,559 --> 00:34:42,329
