You lost your money.

644
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,920
Why are you following me?

645
00:35:29,519 --> 00:35:30,599
They want to arrest me.

646
00:35:30,769 --> 00:35:32,159
What did you do?

647
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:33,679
I didn't do anything wrong.

648
00:35:33,880 --> 00:35:35,559
They accused me of pretending to be the princess.

649
00:35:35,679 --> 00:35:37,679
Why did you do that?

650
00:35:38,159 --> 00:35:39,519
Young lady.

651
00:35:39,519 --> 00:35:41,119
Are you a fool?

652
00:35:41,329 --> 00:35:43,440
I'm not pretending to be a princess. I really...

653
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,400
Open the door!

654
00:35:52,719 --> 00:35:53,719
Open the door!

655
00:35:55,119 --> 00:35:56,159
Coming.

656
00:35:56,159 --> 00:35:57,440
Are you going to pay me if you break the door?

657
00:35:59,559 --> 00:36:00,679
It's still daytime.

658
00:36:00,679 --> 00:36:02,000
What's the rush?

659
00:36:02,199 --> 00:36:03,809
Are you here to buy clothes?

660
00:36:05,039 --> 00:36:06,329
We're chasing after a girl.

661
00:36:06,519 --> 00:36:08,079
I saw her walking on this street.

662
00:36:08,079 --> 00:36:09,079
Have you seen her before?

663
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,519
We're looking for her.

664
00:36:17,809 --> 00:36:18,960
Yes, I have.

665
00:36:20,329 --> 00:36:23,960
This lady was pickpocketed on the street earlier.

666
00:36:23,960 --> 00:36:25,719
She went after the perpetrator, heading south.

667
00:36:26,769 --> 00:36:29,289
Sir, what did she do?

668
00:36:29,289 --> 00:36:31,119
Is she a robber?

669
00:36:31,239 --> 00:36:33,239
This area is not safe lately.

670
00:36:41,119 --> 00:36:42,559
- Search the place. - Hey!

671
00:36:42,559 --> 00:36:44,400
Sir!

672
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:02,289
<i>Great virtue brings happiness</i>

673
00:37:02,289 --> 00:37:03,400
What's the matter?

674
00:37:03,679 --> 00:37:05,880
- I don't know. - What's wrong?

675
00:37:24,440 --> 00:37:25,840
- We didn't find anything. - We didn't find anything.

676
00:37:27,039 --> 00:37:28,039
She's not there either.

677
00:37:29,039 --> 00:37:31,480
Sir, as I said, she's not here.

678
00:37:31,480 --> 00:37:33,679
My textile workshop is operating.

679
00:37:33,809 --> 00:37:36,199
You simply look around the workshop.

680
00:37:36,199 --> 00:37:37,639
It will leave a bad impression.

681
00:37:37,639 --> 00:37:38,679
That's enough.

682
00:37:39,039 --> 00:37:40,199
If you see her again,

683
00:37:40,199 --> 00:37:41,199
inform us right away.

684
00:37:41,599 --> 00:37:42,599
Of course.

685
00:37:43,639 --> 00:37:44,679
Let's go.

686
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,400
You're smart.

687
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:03,519
At least you hid in the tank.

688
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,559
Thank you for the help.

689
00:38:05,769 --> 00:38:07,559
I thought you wouldn't save me.

690
00:38:07,719 --> 00:38:08,719
That's enough.

691
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:10,809
You don't seem like a bad person.

692
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:13,360
They have nothing better to do.

693
00:38:13,519 --> 00:38:15,289
You're just pretending to be a princess.

694
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,480
Do they really have to do that?

695
00:38:16,639 --> 00:38:17,719
Ma'am.

696
00:38:17,719 --> 00:38:18,920
I'm not pretending.

697
00:38:19,159 --> 00:38:20,639
I'm really a princess.

698
00:38:20,639 --> 00:38:21,769
All right.

699
00:38:21,769 --> 00:38:23,880
It doesn't matter if you're a princess or a lord.

700
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:24,880
I need to get back to work.

701
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:26,039
You should go.

702
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:27,440
Ma'am.

703
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:29,400
If I go out right now,

704
00:38:29,519 --> 00:38:30,840
I'll get caught.

705
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:32,039
I beg you.

706
00:38:32,039 --> 00:38:33,679
Please let me stay here for one more day.

707
00:38:33,809 --> 00:38:35,159
I beg you.

708
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:37,639
All right.

709
00:38:37,769 --> 00:38:39,480
Go inside and get changed.

710
00:38:40,079 --> 00:38:41,769
Don't blame me when you get sick.

711
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:44,809
Thank you, ma'am.

712
00:38:56,719 --> 00:38:58,289
So this is the grassland.

713
00:39:00,289 --> 00:39:01,880
It's so vast.

714
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:06,039
Madam Su Yi Li.

715
00:39:06,039 --> 00:39:07,119
Do you have more cheese?

716
00:39:07,119 --> 00:39:09,039
- Please keep some for me. - Sure.

717
00:39:09,039 --> 00:39:10,440
Come to my tent later.

718
00:39:10,559 --> 00:39:11,639
You can have as much as you want.

719
00:39:12,639 --> 00:39:14,769
Your Highness, are there any presents for us?

720
00:39:15,119 --> 00:39:17,480
Ye, everyone gets a present.

721
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:18,960
Ya Luo.

722
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:22,809
Your Highness, the herbs are ready.

723
00:39:22,809 --> 00:39:23,880
Here they are.

724
00:39:25,559 --> 00:39:26,599
Take a look.

725
00:39:27,559 --> 00:39:28,639
It's not bad.

726
00:39:30,679 --> 00:39:32,239
- Here, Your Highness. - Take a look.

727
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:33,480
Help yourself.

728
00:39:33,679 --> 00:39:35,400
- There are presents! - I want this.

729
00:39:38,159 --> 00:39:39,159
This is good.

730
00:39:39,639 --> 00:39:40,719
- Look. - Let me see.

731
00:39:41,769 --> 00:39:43,679
Uncle Shi Min, where is my reward?

732
00:39:43,679 --> 00:39:44,809
- Where is my reward? - Where is my reward?

733
00:39:44,809 --> 00:39:46,329
- Stand still. - Where is my reward?

734
00:39:46,329 --> 00:39:47,440
Stand still and close your eyes.

735
00:39:47,809 --> 00:39:49,039
Close your eyes. Close them.

736
00:39:54,159 --> 00:39:55,719
What about me, Uncle Shi Min? Where's mine?

737
00:39:55,719 --> 00:39:57,079
- Give it to me - I only have one pony.

738
00:39:58,639 --> 00:40:00,880
- I'll give it if you can reach it. - Give it to me, Father!

739
00:40:01,480 --> 00:40:02,519
Give it to me.

740
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:07,400
Father!

741
00:40:12,199 --> 00:40:13,400
Uncle Shi Min!

742
00:40:13,559 --> 00:40:15,480
Father, don't go against your words.

743
00:40:15,480 --> 00:40:16,480
Father!

744
00:40:17,199 --> 00:40:18,289
Uncle Shi Min!

745
00:40:20,440 --> 00:40:21,920
Give it to me, Uncle Shi Min!

746
00:40:22,159 --> 00:40:23,289
You promised me!

747
00:40:30,519 --> 00:40:32,159
- Here, let me help you. - Thank you.

748
00:40:32,639 --> 00:40:33,679
Not bad.

749
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,039
That was fun.

750
00:40:36,809 --> 00:40:37,840
Hey!

751
00:40:39,809 --> 00:40:41,199
You're good in Cuju, right?

752
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:42,960
This is for you.

753
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:46,039
Can we have the ball?

754
00:40:52,079 --> 00:40:53,079
Here.

755
00:40:55,119 --> 00:40:56,519
- Stop right there! - Come on!

756
00:40:56,519 --> 00:40:57,519
Wait for me!

757
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:00,199
Slow down!

758
00:41:00,599 --> 00:41:02,000
- Give it to me. - No.

759
00:41:04,519 --> 00:41:05,840
I'll send the present home for them.

760
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:07,480
- Hold it properly. - Can you take it to him?

761
00:41:22,329 --> 00:41:24,159
The pay is so low.

762
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:26,360
Madam Zhang, you should consider yourself lucky.

763
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,920
At least we still have work to do.

764
00:41:27,920 --> 00:41:28,960
We won't be starving to death.

765
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:30,039
That's not bad.

766
00:41:30,809 --> 00:41:31,840
You're right.

767
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:33,559
It's getting difficult to use the machine.

768
00:41:33,679 --> 00:41:34,809
Yes.

769
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:43,920
Madam Chai.

770
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,519
You finally hired someone.

771
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:47,519
I found her on the street.

772
00:41:47,519 --> 00:41:48,639
She'll leave tomorrow.

773
00:41:54,880 --> 00:41:56,440
Greetings, everyone.

774
00:41:58,079 --> 00:41:59,639
What are you looking at?

775
00:41:59,639 --> 00:42:00,639
Get back to work!

776
00:42:05,599 --> 00:42:07,440
She's so pretty.

777
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:10,329
What kind of salutation was that?

778
00:42:10,329 --> 00:42:12,809
I don't know. It looks nice though.

779
00:42:12,809 --> 00:42:13,809
Exactly.

780
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:15,329
Greetings, everyone.

781
00:42:15,329 --> 00:42:16,329
That's not correct.

782
00:42:16,329 --> 00:42:17,440
It's like this.

783
00:42:17,559 --> 00:42:19,559
- No. - That's what she did.

784
00:42:21,289 --> 00:42:22,880
You'll sleep here tonight.

785
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:24,679
You have to leave tomorrow.

786
00:42:24,920 --> 00:42:26,289
I don't feed people for nothing.

787
00:42:26,840 --> 00:42:28,289
Thank you, ma'am.

788
00:42:28,289 --> 00:42:30,199
I will repay you someday.

789
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,599
Thank you.

790
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:43,039
What should I do tomorrow?

791
00:42:43,639 --> 00:42:45,960
<i>Yunzhou County Office</i>

792
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:53,360
What did you say?

793
00:42:54,769 --> 00:42:55,840
I didn't hear it clearly.

794
00:42:56,360 --> 00:42:58,639
Please pardon me.

795
00:42:58,639 --> 00:42:59,769
Princess Yong'an...

796
00:42:59,769 --> 00:43:01,880
We lost her.

797
00:43:03,639 --> 00:43:05,400
It's fine if you can't find her.

798
00:43:05,559 --> 00:43:06,840
What do you mean you lost her?

799
00:43:06,840 --> 00:43:10,559
We saw a lady who looks like her on the street.

800
00:43:10,559 --> 00:43:13,480
But she got away.

801
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:14,719
A lady who looks like her?

802
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:16,079
How did she run away?

803
00:43:16,400 --> 00:43:18,840
Mr. Wei, we'll keep looking.

804
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:22,159
However, Princess Yong'an has feet.

805
00:43:22,289 --> 00:43:23,840
We are unsure...

806
00:43:23,840 --> 00:43:25,960
whether she's still in Yunzhou or not.

807
00:43:25,960 --> 00:43:27,400
How dare you absolve yourself?

808
00:43:27,599 --> 00:43:28,679
Yes.

809
00:43:28,679 --> 00:43:30,960
We'll keep looking.

810
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:33,239
- I'll look for her tomorrow! - I'll look for her tomorrow!

811
00:43:33,519 --> 00:43:34,559
- Get lost! - Get lost!

812
00:43:34,559 --> 00:43:35,559
Yes, sir!

813
00:43:40,519 --> 00:43:41,599
Yan Er.

814
00:43:42,480 --> 00:43:43,559
Where are you?

